      "factorType": "Software quality assurance",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Simulation software (Ansys Mechanical 2021 R2) must be under documented version control with traceable release notes and regression test suite results on file.",
      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical 2021 R2 is a commercially validated FEA solver with published verification and validation documentation. Version control records, installation qualification logs, and regression test results were reviewed and confirmed compliant with FDA 21 CFR Part 11 requirements. Achieved level 3 exceeds required level 2."
